<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateGroupNode.PolygonWindingOrder" Title="PolygonWindingOrder enumeration" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateGroupNode">IStateGroupNode</PageRef> ->
    PolygonWindingOrder
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>PolygonWindingOrder</TypeRef> enumeration specifies which vertex winding order is treated as front-facing by an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateGroupNode">IStateGroupNode</PageRef>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <EnumMemberList>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Clockwise">
        Treats triangles whose vertices wind clockwise in framebuffer space as front-facing.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="CounterClockwise">
        Treats triangles whose vertices wind counter-clockwise in framebuffer space as front-facing.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
    </EnumMemberList>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateGroupNode.SetPolygonWindingOrder">IStateGroupNode.SetPolygonWindingOrder</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
